title: Taylor Swift Loves To Sing About Rain!
description:
Taylor Swift has themes in her songs, and rain is one of them! Why does she like to include rain in her songs? And what picture is she trying to paint in every song when she mentions it? Amy, Nick, Lacey and Ana break it down!
What did we miss? What should we break down next? Let us know!
